Spabreaks.com is a multi-award winning spa booking platform working with more than 500 spas in the UK and Ireland, arranging spa escapes for up to 250,000 people each year. We were founded on the principle of making spa experiences more accessible, and to bring back the ancient purpose of spas as places of sanctuary for mind and body. With over 5,000 spa experiences to choose from, starting from as little as £16, you’re guaranteed to find the perfect spa escape